                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d65">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-11-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 28, 1894</hi>
                        </date>. (Received November 30.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The new minister for foreign affairs has flour claims under consideration, and
                    promises definite conclusion in a few days.</p>
            </div>
